--- Summary by Developer ---
The configuration 'AREA' plays a crucial role in the system, specifically in the context of SVG (Scalable Vector Graphics) document processing. It is related to the `KEY_AOI` hint, which represents the Area of Interest. The `KEY_AOI` hint is used to retrieve the Area of Interest (AOI) from the hints map, and it is utilized in various methods to handle the AOI transformation matrix.

